    "sensesNotes": "Darkvision 60 ft, Keen Smell",
    "tactics": "Giant rats rely on Pack Tactics and numbers. They swarm lone targets, attempting to spread disease through repeated bites.",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Bite [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 4 + Melee Combat 2), Reach: 5 ft\n<ul>\n<li><strong><em>Margin 1:</strong></em> 3 damage (Small size, light natural weapon: 4 - 1 = 3)</li>\n<li><strong><em>Margin 2:</strong></em> 5 damage (3 + 2 Str)</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Special Abilities:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Pack Tactics:</strong> When an ally is within 5 feet of the target, subtract 1 from both attack dice</li>\n<li><strong>Keen Smell:</strong> Scent-based Perception checks have Fortune</li>\n<li><strong>Disease Carrier:</strong> On hit with margin 2, target must make Fortitude save (1 success needed) or contract Filth Fever\n<ul>\n<li><strong><em>Incubation:</strong></em> 1d8 days</li>\n<li><strong><em>Effect:</strong></em> Poisoned condition until cured</li>\n<li><strong><em>Cure:</strong></em> Two consecutive successful Fortitude saves (1/day) OR magical healing</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Pack Tactics:</strong> When an ally is within 5 feet of the target, subtract 1 from both attack dice\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Keen Smell:</strong> Scent-based Perception checks have Fortune</li>\n<li><strong>Disease Carrier:</strong> On hit with margin 2, target must make Fortitude save (1 success needed) or contract Filth Fever\n<ul>\n<li><strong><em>Incubation:</strong></em> 1d8 days</li>\n<li><strong><em>Effect:</strong></em> Poisoned condition until cured</li>\n<li><strong><em>Cure:</strong></em> Two consecutive successful Fortitude saves (1/day) OR magical healing</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
